<p>I've long pounded the desk saying that the purpose of XML is best for machine-to-machine vendor-neutral hierarchical non-binary data representation, and the further you stray from any one of those points, you lose.</p>

<p>I will not ever use DocBook, at least not as an input method.  I do not want to edit configuration files in XML.  XML is just far too verbose for me to write, and barely not-quite-enough verbose for me to tolerate reading.</p>
